          "category": "Calculation",
          "estimatedDuration": 5,
          "businessRationale": "Real-time calculation with scenario modelling (e.g., itemised vs standard deduction) helps taxpayers optimise their filing position. Accurate engine reduces amended returns that cost $100+ each to process.",
