          "estimatedDuration": 480,
          "businessRationale": "Assessment is the most resource-intensive step; timely assessments reduce cycle time and supplier costs. Long assessment delays increase customer dissatisfaction and raise churn risk, while rushed assessments increase overpayment risk.",
